{"tid":2437361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[Copy & Paste]  國泰太古先後表態支持「愛國者治港」","createTime":"2021-03-07T23:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T00:38:30.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f00d4d6ae361b35ada377f4b54de3e8e176ee845","tid":2437361,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:26:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">國泰支持「愛國者治港」 會繼續投資於香港</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/2015484\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2015484&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=a28f3c51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2015484&h=210b4a19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/2015484</a><br />\n<br />\n就傳媒查詢有關「愛國者治港」原則，國泰航空集團發言人回應指，國泰航空支持「愛國者治港」原則。這是「一國兩制」下的一個重要元素，而「一國兩制」是香港繁榮穩定的基石 。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">國泰重申，作為香港商界的一份子，相信「愛國者治港」原則有利於香港作為世界級商業及金融中心的發展。</span></span></strong>國泰一直以香港為家，會繼續投資於香港，對香港的承諾始終堅定不移。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">太古支持「愛國者治港」 有利作為商業金融中心發展</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/2015481/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2015481%2F&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=87c9a719\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2015481%2F&h=d7c25402\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/2015481/</a><br />\n<br />\n就傳媒查詢有關「愛國者治港」原則，太古公司發言人指，太古支持「愛國者治港」原則。這是「一國兩制」下的一個重要元素，而「一國兩制」是香港繁榮穩定的基石。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n發言人強調，太古作為香港商界的一份子，集團相信此原則有利於香港作為世界級商業及金融中心的發展。</span></span></strong>過去150年以來，太古一直以香港為家。太古會繼續投資於香港，對香港的承諾始終堅定不移。"},{"pid":"c56dba5ed8642aee5245f1ada7ac5ee5b39ca37b","tid":2437361,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4efa7021051f76adf1c0a946a2ae74cda61a96","tid":2437361,"uid":63863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:45:01.000Z","msg":"有得佢唔支持咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔支持連香港航權都收返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2680c968741ef5b87b09623147a1a0a06ee19db0","tid":2437361,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:50:30.000Z","msg":"做生意嘅嘢搵錢行先"},{"pid":"0d279eef96c166577f459501c857ae6c3ac33419","tid":2437361,"uid":106026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:52:27.000Z","msg":"國泰同太古成班管理層都係英國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d0fc381530dc625f7641ca6648e841febedf3d","tid":2437361,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d279eef96c166577f459501c857ae6c3ac33419","tid":2437361,"uid":106026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:52:27.000Z","msg":"國泰同太古成班管理層都係英國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:53:55.000Z","msg":"宣誓咗未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛中国定愛英國<i